title: PDF Form Character Sheet D&D 4e
description:
This is the best character sheet I have ever come across. It's a PDF form, allowing you to enter the values with Adobe Acrobat and it auto-calculates the derived values, much like other character sheets I've seen created with Excel. The difference is it doesn't look nearly as ugly as those Excel based character sheets. 

If you're looking for anything else for 4e check here: http://thepiratebay.se/torrent/4700086
